---------------------------------------------------------
Known bugs that need to be fixed:
---------------------------------------------------------
* weight treatment in TPrincipal (?)



---------------------------------------------------------
Improvements foreseen for TMVA4:
---------------------------------------------------------
* transformation of variables subsets
* cross validation
* automatic parameter tuning
* simple example scripts
* automatic variable relevance determination/variable selection
* meaningful MethodBase::TestMulticlass() and ResultsMulticlass
* Likelihood with Multiclass feature (requested by ATLAS-tau group)
* remove incompatibility of multiclass and TMVAGui.C

---------------------------------------------------------
Features we would like to have in future versions of TMVA:
(mostly taken from Peters "wishlist")
---------------------------------------------------------
* separate training and application for all methods (using separate classes)
* application code in separate library which is ROOT-independent
* simplified data input/output interface for all methods
* get rid of MakeClass
* possibility to chain methods
* treatment of errors
* test-driven design ;)
 